<font color="yellow">English: DramaFever</font>

2
00:00:05,024 --> 00:00:08,524
<font color="yellow">Bahasa Indonesia: niniiinggg</font>

3
00:00:09,800 --> 00:00:14,900
<font color="yellow"><i>[Kemiripan terhadap segala kisah atau kejadian bersejarah hanyalah fiktif.]</i></font>

4
00:00:15,599 --> 00:00:17,600
<font color="yellow"><i>[Episode 19]</i></font>

5
00:00:22,257 --> 00:00:25,158
<font color="yellow">Yeon Hui. Yeon Hui!</font>

6
00:00:45,057 --> 00:00:47,457
<font color="yellow">Nyalakan apinya!</font>

7
00:01:30,858 --> 00:01:33,658
<font color="yellow">Hei! Diamlah!</font>

8
00:02:12,358 --> 00:02:16,057
<font color="yellow">- Wah, lihat langitnya!
- Awannya!</font>

9
00:03:58,157 --> 00:04:03,057
<font color="yellow">Yang Mulia! Yang Mulia!</font>

10
00:04:03,057 --> 00:04:06,157
<font color="yellow">Yang Mulia baik-baik saja?</font>

11
00:04:06,858 --> 00:04:10,657
<font color="yellow"><i>Raja! Jangan bunug putri!</i></font>

12
00:04:10,657 --> 00:04:14,258
<font color="yellow">Jika dibunuh, keluarga kerajaan akan terkena kutukan!</font>

13
00:04:14,258 --> 00:04:17,658
<font color="yellow"><i>Begitulah kutukanmu terjadi.</i></font>

14
00:04:17,658 --> 00:04:23,358
<font color="yellow">Kau cuma perlu kembalikan kutukannya ke tempat ini, tempat asalnya.</font>

15
00:05:49,858 --> 00:05:54,057
<font color="yellow">Raja tiba!</font>

16
00:05:59,158 --> 00:06:02,158
<font color="yellow">Apakah tujuan akhir Hong Joo membunuh putri</font>

17
00:06:02,158 --> 00:06:07,257
<font color="yellow">dan mengutuk keluarga kerajaan untuk berusaha mengakhirinya?</font>

18
00:06:07,858 --> 00:06:11,057
<font color="yellow">Itu sebabnya Putri harus diselamatkan! Tolong, Yang Mulia!</font>

19
00:06:11,057 --> 00:06:16,257
<font color="yellow">Tolong, cepat lepaskan hamba! Waktunya cuma sedikit!</font>

20
00:06:54,757 --> 00:06:58,057
<font color="yellow"><i>Dia bukan Yeon Hui, ingat?</i></font>

21
00:06:58,057 --> 00:07:02,757
<font color="yellow"><i>Bukan salahmu. Tapi salah mereka yang menghinamu.</i></font>

22
00:07:02,757 --> 00:07:06,658
<font color="yellow"><i>Luapkanlah kebencianmu pada mereka!</i></font>

23
00:07:06,658 --> 00:07:09,757
<font color="yellow"><i>Bunuh saja anak yang terkena kutukan itu</i></font>

24
00:07:09,757 --> 00:07:13,057
<font color="yellow"><i>agar kembali jadi Yeon Hui yang manis dan polos seperti dulu!</i></font>

25
00:07:13,057 --> 00:07:18,158
<font color="yellow"><i>Makhluk itu bukan Yeon Hui.  Cuma makhluk terkutuk!</i></font>

26
00:07:18,158 --> 00:07:23,358
<font color="yellow"><i>Jika kutukannya disingkirkan dari tubuhnya, dia akan kembali seperti dulu!</i></font>

27
00:07:23,358 --> 00:07:28,057
<font color="yellow"><i>Hanya engkau yang bisa melepaskan dia dari kutukan jahat itu!</i></font>

28
00:07:28,057 --> 00:07:31,458
<font color="yellow">Hanya engkau yang bisa lindungi Yeon Hui!</font>

29
00:07:40,557 --> 00:07:42,557
<font color="yellow">Yeon Hui.</font>

30
00:08:16,057 --> 00:08:18,358
<font color="yellow">Yeon Hui!</font>

31
00:08:19,458 --> 00:08:22,057
<font color="yellow">- Ada apa?
- Ada apa?</font>

32
00:08:22,057 --> 00:08:27,557
<font color="yellow">Yeon Hui! Yeon Hui! Yeon Hui! Yeon Hui!</font>

33
00:08:29,057 --> 00:08:34,057
<font color="yellow">Yeon Hui! Yeon Hui! Bangun, Yeon Hui!</font>

34
00:08:37,457 --> 00:08:40,158
<font color="yellow">Yeon Hui!</font>

35
00:10:18,857 --> 00:10:21,758
<font color="yellow">- Ratu Park!
- Yang Mulia!</font>

36
00:10:21,758 --> 00:10:23,273
<font color="yellow">- Cepat panggil dokter!
- Ya!</font>

37
00:10:40,658 --> 00:10:43,658
<font color="yellow">Kenapa kau lakukan itu?</font>

38
00:10:44,357 --> 00:10:48,258
<font color="yellow">Kenapa kau bahayakan dirimu?</font>

39
00:11:02,158 --> 00:11:05,057
<font color="yellow">Aku tak bisa menyelamatkannya.</font>

40
00:11:08,057 --> 00:11:10,957
<font color="yellow">Ibuku, maksudku.</font>

41
00:11:14,758 --> 00:11:18,658
<font color="yellow">Aku sangat takut takkan bisa melakukan apapun lagi.</font>

42
00:11:18,658 --> 00:11:24,357
<font color="yellow">Aku sangat takut tak bisa melakukan apapun untukmu.</font>

43
00:11:29,057 --> 00:11:31,957
<font color="yellow">Aku takut itu terjadi.</font>

44
00:13:18,857 --> 00:13:21,957
<font color="yellow">Seberapa parah luka Rahib?</font>

45
00:13:21,957 --> 00:13:23,957
<font color="yellow">Hampir mati, tapi masih selamat.</font>

46
00:13:23,957 --> 00:13:25,658
<font color="yellow">Itu lho, orang yang namanya "Pak Choi"...</font>

47
00:13:25,658 --> 00:13:28,557
<font color="yellow">Tampaknya dia sedang tak sehat.</font>

48
00:13:31,357 --> 00:13:34,057
<font color="yellow">Jangan  beritahu Yeon Hui.</font>

49
00:13:37,057 --> 00:13:39,357
<font color="yellow">- Tuan Heo.
- Rahib!</font>

50
00:13:40,057 --> 00:13:42,557
<font color="yellow">Baik-baik saja?</font>

51
00:13:43,957 --> 00:13:46,158
<font color="yellow">Yeon Hui?</font>

52
00:13:46,158 --> 00:13:50,057
<font color="yellow">Dia selamat. Sedang tidur di kamarnya sekarang.</font>

53
00:13:52,658 --> 00:13:54,857
<font color="yellow">Syukurlah.</font>

54
00:13:54,857 --> 00:13:59,158
<font color="yellow">Kenapa Pak Choi menyerangmu?</font>

55
00:14:02,158 --> 00:14:06,057
<font color="yellow">Kenapa mulut sialanmu itu tak bisa diam?</font>

56
00:14:06,758 --> 00:14:11,057
<font color="yellow">Tentu saja karena "itu."</font>

57
00:14:11,057 --> 00:14:14,357
<font color="yellow">Bukannya dia bilang mau ambil sesuatu?</font>

58
00:14:14,357 --> 00:14:17,258
<font color="yellow">- Apa, ya?
- Soon Deuk!</font>

59
00:14:17,758 --> 00:14:21,658
<font color="yellow">Ayo, Soon Deuk! Sakit sekali!</font>

60
00:14:21,658 --> 00:14:25,158
<font color="yellow">Sepertinya kau harus obati lukaku lagi.</font>

61
00:14:25,158 --> 00:14:27,357
<font color="yellow">Sungguh sakit!</font>

62
00:14:35,258 --> 00:14:37,357
<font color="yellow">Yeon Hui!</font>

63
00:14:39,957 --> 00:14:42,158
<font color="yellow">Mau ke mana dengan kondisi begitu?</font>

64
00:14:42,158 --> 00:14:45,557
<font color="yellow">Ke kastil. Pasti sesuatu terjadi di sana.</font>

65
00:14:45,557 --> 00:14:50,158
<font color="yellow">Aku terima peringatan katanya bayi kerajaan dalam bahaya.</font>

66
00:14:50,158 --> 00:14:55,057
<font color="yellow">Aku harus cek apakah bayi Ratu Park baik-baik saja.</font>

67
00:14:57,057 --> 00:14:59,557
<font color="yellow">Kau takkan dengarkan aku meski kucoba hentikan, ya kan?</font>

68
00:15:31,057 --> 00:15:32,957
<font color="yellow">Buka gerbangnya!</font>

69
00:15:36,158 --> 00:15:40,057
<font color="yellow">Mereka menunggu Putri kalau-kalau kembali ke kastil</font>

70
00:15:40,057 --> 00:15:46,557
<font color="yellow">lalu menyuruhku menunggu di sini agar bisa mengantarkan Putri dengan aman.</font>

71
00:15:47,258 --> 00:15:51,357
<font color="yellow">Aku ingin bertemu Ratu Suri.</font>

72
00:15:51,357 --> 00:15:56,957
<font color="yellow">Akan sulit menemuinya, karena beliau masih sakit dan beristirahat.</font>

73
00:16:20,758 --> 00:16:22,658
<font color="yellow">Ratu.</font>

74
00:16:27,258 --> 00:16:29,758
<font color="yellow">Apa yang terjadi?</font>

75
00:16:30,658 --> 00:16:35,357
<font color="yellow">Ratu keguguran.</font>

76
00:18:00,258 --> 00:18:03,557
<font color="yellow">Baiklah. Mau buat sesuatu?</font>

77
00:18:12,657 --> 00:18:14,057
<font color="yellow">Ini!</font>

78
00:18:30,157 --> 00:18:34,258
<font color="yellow">Hei! Duh!</font>

79
00:18:58,357 --> 00:19:01,657
<font color="yellow">Tolong berikan ini pada Ratu.</font>

80
00:19:01,657 --> 00:19:04,557
<font color="yellow">Obat untuk mengurangi kekhawatirannya.</font>

81
00:19:07,057 --> 00:19:11,157
<font color="yellow">Mungkin beliaulah yang paling takut karena semua ini</font>

82
00:19:11,157 --> 00:19:17,657
<font color="yellow">jadi hamba buatkan ini dengan harapan beliau bisa merasa agak baikan.</font>

83
00:19:17,657 --> 00:19:20,057
<font color="yellow">Kau merendahkanku?</font>

84
00:19:21,758 --> 00:19:25,357
<font color="yellow">Hamba merendahkan juga membenci Yang Mulia.</font>

85
00:19:25,357 --> 00:19:30,157
<font color="yellow">Hamba lakukan ini hanya karena merasa iba melihat Yang Mulia kehilangan anak.</font>

86
00:19:31,057 --> 00:19:34,258
<font color="yellow">Hamba buatkan ini bukan untuk Yang Mulia.</font>

87
00:19:36,357 --> 00:19:43,657
<font color="yellow">Jika wabah masih menyebar, rakyat akan terus menghinamu.</font>

88
00:19:43,657 --> 00:19:46,857
<font color="yellow">Mengingat wabahnya, yang sudah menyebabkan malapetaka di tanah kita ini</font>

89
00:19:46,857 --> 00:19:53,458
<font color="yellow">disalahkan pada Putri, bisa jadi ini karena sihir hitam Hong Joo.</font>

90
00:19:53,458 --> 00:19:59,057
<font color="yellow">Jika memang benar, semua akan membaik begitu Putri hancurkan kutukannya.</font>

91
00:20:00,258 --> 00:20:06,357
<font color="yellow">Memangnya kutukannya bisa dihancurkan?</font>

92
00:20:08,958 --> 00:20:15,258
<font color="yellow">Semua ini karena kelemahanku hingga aku percaya Hong Joo.</font>

93
00:20:15,258 --> 00:20:19,458
<font color="yellow">Karena itu juga aku kehilangan anakku.</font>

94
00:20:20,758 --> 00:20:24,758
<font color="yellow">Takkan pernah kubiarkan terjadi seperti ini lagi.</font>

95
00:20:24,758 --> 00:20:28,657
<font color="yellow">Itu sebabnya, kuberikan kalian berdua tanggung jawab untuk menghukumnya.</font>

96
00:20:28,657 --> 00:20:33,958
<font color="yellow">Minta saja padaku jika butuh sesuatu.</font>

97
00:20:33,958 --> 00:20:39,657
<font color="yellow">Yang Mulia berubah pikiran saja sudah sangat membantu.</font>

98
00:20:42,657 --> 00:20:44,857
<font color="yellow">Choi Poong Yeon bilang bahwa dia akan mundur</font>

99
00:20:44,857 --> 00:20:49,458
<font color="yellow">dari jabatannya sebagai pimpinan Cabang Taoist Kerajaan, dan dia akan pergi.</font>

100
00:20:49,458 --> 00:20:51,657
<font color="yellow">Temuilah dia.</font>

101
00:21:11,057 --> 00:21:13,557
<font color="yellow">Kakak! Ini Yeon Hui!</font>

102
00:21:13,557 --> 00:21:15,857
<font color="yellow">Kakak!</font>

103
00:21:16,657 --> 00:21:20,557
<font color="yellow">Tolong keluar temui aku! Aku sungguh baik-baik saja!</font>

104
00:21:34,057 --> 00:21:37,057
<font color="yellow">Semua ini bukan salahmu.</font>

105
00:21:37,057 --> 00:21:39,958
<font color="yellow">Lihatlah, aku tak apa!</font>

106
00:21:40,657 --> 00:21:44,657
<font color="yellow">Kakak! Kakak!</font>

107
00:21:44,657 --> 00:21:47,258
<font color="yellow"><i>Yeon Hui.</i></font>

108
00:21:50,657 --> 00:21:56,857
<font color="yellow"><i>Aku takkan pernah lagi menemuimu.</i></font>

109
00:22:02,258 --> 00:22:07,157
<font color="yellow"><i>Tidak... Aku tak boleh menemuimu lagi.</i></font>

110
00:22:09,057 --> 00:22:11,657
<font color="yellow"><i>Maaf.</i></font>

111
00:23:18,258 --> 00:23:20,157
<font color="yellow">Yang Mulia.</font>

112
00:23:20,157 --> 00:23:23,258
<font color="yellow">Putri tiba.</font>

113
00:23:48,758 --> 00:23:52,357
<font color="yellow">Aku tak bisa memahami Ratu.</font>

114
00:23:53,758 --> 00:23:56,657
<font color="yellow">Bagaimanapun...</font>

115
00:23:56,657 --> 00:24:04,157
<font color="yellow">akan kucoba mengerti kenapa Ratu bertindak sejauh itu demi punya anak.</font>

116
00:24:07,857 --> 00:24:10,557
<font color="yellow">Semoga Ratu sehat selamanya.</font>

117
00:24:12,657 --> 00:24:15,057
<font color="yellow">Yeon Hui.</font>

118
00:24:18,258 --> 00:24:23,057
<font color="yellow">Pokoknya kau harus hancurkan kutukan ini.</font>

119
00:24:24,157 --> 00:24:30,157
<font color="yellow">Harus, dan jalanilah hidup sesuai keinginanmu.</font>

120
00:24:32,357 --> 00:24:38,057
<font color="yellow">Cuma itu mauku.</font>

121
00:24:42,857 --> 00:24:47,657
<font color="yellow">Ya, Ibu.</font>

122
00:25:32,758 --> 00:25:35,657
<font color="yellow">"Semua sudah selesai sekarang."</font>

123
00:25:35,657 --> 00:25:39,057
<font color="yellow">"Hentikan, Hong Joo."</font>

124
00:25:39,057 --> 00:25:42,057
<font color="yellow">Pasti kau mau bilang begitu, Pak Choi.</font>

125
00:25:46,157 --> 00:25:48,458
<font color="yellow">Semua sudah berakhir.</font>

126
00:25:48,458 --> 00:25:51,458
<font color="yellow">Aku hampir berhasil!</font>

127
00:25:52,157 --> 00:25:56,458
<font color="yellow">Makanya tak  bisa berhenti sekarang.</font>

128
00:26:08,758 --> 00:26:14,657
<font color="yellow">Bawa halaman terakhir Kutukan Grimoire?</font>

129
00:26:14,657 --> 00:26:17,657
<font color="yellow">Pasti ada sesuatu tertulis di situ.</font>

130
00:26:17,657 --> 00:26:19,857
<font color="yellow">Iya, kan?</font>

131
00:26:22,357 --> 00:26:24,958
<font color="yellow">Tolong berikan padaku.</font>

132
00:28:15,758 --> 00:28:20,157
<font color="yellow">Aku dengar kabar Tuan meninggalkan Cabang Taoist Kerajaan.</font>

133
00:28:20,157 --> 00:28:26,857
<font color="yellow">Aku mungkin bisa membahayakan Yeon Hui lagi. Mana mungkin aku tetap di sisinya?</font>

134
00:28:26,857 --> 00:28:31,357
<font color="yellow">Yeon Hui sadar Tuan tak bisa lakukan apapun akan masalah itu.</font>

135
00:28:31,357 --> 00:28:37,657
<font color="yellow">Tidak. Toh akhirnya, aku tak bisa mengontrol emosiku sendiri.</font>

136
00:28:38,657 --> 00:28:45,458
<font color="yellow">Tapi, yang lebih kutakutkan adalah bagian dari diriku yang terus berusaha menyakitinya.</font>

137
00:28:49,458 --> 00:28:52,458
<font color="yellow">Aku bahkan tak tahu lagi.</font>

138
00:29:03,357 --> 00:29:08,057
<font color="yellow">Ini obat agar bisa melihat sekilas ke dalam hatimu sendiri.</font>

139
00:29:08,057 --> 00:29:13,057
<font color="yellow">Semoag bisa menolong.</font>

140
00:29:50,657 --> 00:29:53,057
<font color="yellow"><i>- Aku akan melindungimu.
- Baik-baik saja?</i></font>

141
00:29:53,057 --> 00:29:54,157
<font color="yellow"><i>Aku akan di sisimu dan melindungimu!</i></font>

142
00:29:54,157 --> 00:29:57,357
<font color="yellow"><i>Aku akan... melindungimu.</i></font>

143
00:30:00,458 --> 00:30:01,958
<font color="yellow"><i>Poong Yeon.</i></font>

144
00:30:01,958 --> 00:30:04,458
<font color="yellow">Kau pegang erat Putri?</font>

145
00:30:04,458 --> 00:30:09,857
<font color="yellow">Ya, Ayah. Jangan khawatir. Kupegang erat Putri.</font>

146
00:30:09,857 --> 00:30:12,157
<font color="yellow">Aku pasti takkan melepaskannya.</font>

147
00:30:15,258 --> 00:30:18,057
<font color="yellow">Kau harus lindungi Yeon Hui.</font>

148
00:30:18,057 --> 00:30:19,857
<font color="yellow">Paham?</font>

149
00:30:19,857 --> 00:30:25,958
<font color="yellow">Ya. Aku akan berada di sisi Yeon Hui.</font>

150
00:30:25,958 --> 00:30:29,857
<font color="yellow">Akan kulindungi Yeon Hui sepanjang hidupku.</font>

151
00:30:29,857 --> 00:30:33,657
<font color="yellow"><i>Apakah permintaanku untuk melindunginya membuatmu tertekan?</i></font>

152
00:30:36,857 --> 00:30:38,857
<font color="yellow">Ayah!</font>

153
00:30:38,857 --> 00:30:42,157
<font color="yellow">Terlalu beratah menanggungnya?</font>

154
00:30:42,157 --> 00:30:47,258
<font color="yellow">Ayahlah yang memintaku melindungi Yeon Hui saat dia masih kecil.</font>

155
00:30:47,258 --> 00:30:50,857
<font color="yellow">Makanya aku jadi seseorang yang harus melindungi Yeon Hui selamanya.</font>

156
00:30:50,857 --> 00:30:54,057
<font color="yellow">Tak pernah aku menyuruhmu melindunginya sepanjang hidupmu.</font>

157
00:30:54,057 --> 00:30:56,857
<font color="yellow">Bagaimana bisa kau berpikir begitu?</font>

158
00:30:59,458 --> 00:31:02,057
<font color="yellow">Karena dia adalah seseorang yang harus kulindungi.</font>

159
00:31:02,057 --> 00:31:06,958
<font color="yellow">Bukankah itu artinya aku harus bertanggung jawab padanya?</font>

160
00:31:06,958 --> 00:31:09,958
<font color="yellow">Kau bingung membedakan tanggung jawab dengan cinta?</font>

161
00:31:10,657 --> 00:31:12,458
<font color="yellow">Tidak.</font>

162
00:31:12,458 --> 00:31:15,057
<font color="yellow">Perasaanku pada Yeon Hui tulus.</font>

163
00:31:15,057 --> 00:31:19,958
<font color="yellow">Ingin kulindungi dia karena kusayang dia.</font>

164
00:31:21,458 --> 00:31:24,057
<font color="yellow">Tapi pada akhirnya kau tak bisa melindunginya.</font>

165
00:31:25,700 --> 00:31:28,000
<font color="yellow">Itu bukan...</font>

166
00:31:30,200 --> 00:31:32,798
<font color="yellow">karena perasaanku padanya tidaklah cukup.</font>

167
00:31:35,598 --> 00:31:38,400
<font color="yellow">Tapi karena kau mulai berjalan di jalan yang salah.</font>

168
00:31:38,400 --> 00:31:42,298
<font color="yellow">Karena keinginanmu untuk melindunginya, bukan karena cintamu padanya</font>

169
00:31:42,298 --> 00:31:45,798
<font color="yellow">hingga kau terobsesi pada Yeon Hui.</font>

170
00:31:49,000 --> 00:31:51,798
<font color="yellow">Menurutmu kau bisa melepaskannya skearang?</font>

171
00:33:11,200 --> 00:33:13,598
<font color="yellow">Lihat aku.</font>

172
00:33:22,000 --> 00:33:27,000
<font color="yellow">Aku takut Kakak bakal bilang takkan pernah menemuiku lagi.</font>

173
00:33:27,000 --> 00:33:31,400
<font color="yellow">Maaf.</font>

174
00:33:31,400 --> 00:33:36,400
<font color="yellow">Aku bilang ingin melindungimu, tapi malah menyakitimu.</font>

175
00:33:38,400 --> 00:33:42,798
<font color="yellow">Kupikir aku harus selalu di sisimu dan melindungimu.</font>

176
00:33:44,400 --> 00:33:46,400
<font color="yellow">Kakak.</font>

177
00:33:47,700 --> 00:33:51,798
<font color="yellow">Kukira aku harus di sisimu, apapun yang terjadi.</font>

178
00:33:52,700 --> 00:33:56,900
<font color="yellow">Kupikir itulah yang terbaik untukmu</font>

